<task id="AIPL-052" project="AI Platform Foundation Phase 1">
  <metadata>
    <title>C3: Implement ChatSessionManager + ChatHistoryManager</title>
    <phase>4 — Workstream C: SprkChat &amp; Agent Framework</phase>
    <tags>bff-api, api, agent-framework, dataverse, redis</tags>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <estimated-effort>4 hours</estimated-effort>
    <dependencies>AIPL-051, AIPL-001</dependencies>
    <blocks>AIPL-054 (ChatEndpoints)</blocks>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Implement ChatSessionManager and ChatHistoryManager to provide persistent, resumable
    chat sessions with a Redis hot cache and Dataverse cold storage.

    Architecture:
    - Redis: hot cache of active sessions (24h TTL per NFR-07)
    - Dataverse sprk_aichatmessage: permanent message history for audit
    - Summarization trigger: after 15 messages, summarize to sprk_aichatsummary
    - Max 50 messages before archive (NFR-12)

    Sessions persist across server restarts. Users can resume a session from any server instance.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    Senior .NET developer familiar with Redis IDistributedCache, Dataverse integration patterns,
    and the chat session schema defined in task 001.
  </role>

  <goal>
    Chat sessions persist in Dataverse and cache in Redis. Sessions resume after server restart.
    Summarization triggers after 15 messages. ChatHistoryManager reads/writes message history.
    Unit tests pass.
  </goal>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-009">Redis IDistributedCache; tenant-scoped keys: "chat:session:{tenantId}:{sessionId}"</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-014">Cache keys versioned by model + content version</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">24-hour idle TTL (NFR-07); max 50 messages per session before archive (NFR-12)</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">Summarize after 15 messages; summary stored in sprk_aichatsummary</constraint>
    <constraint source="AIPL-001">Schema: sprk_aichatmessage, sprk_aichatsummary as defined in task 001</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>projects/ai-spaarke-platform-enhancements-r1/spec.md</file>
      <file>projects/ai-spaarke-platform-enhancements-r1/notes/design/dataverse-chat-schema.md</file>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/SprkChatAgent.cs</file>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-009-redis-caching.md</file>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-014-ai-caching.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="Read chat entity schema from task 001">
      Read notes/design/dataverse-chat-schema.md (created in task 001) for the exact field
      names and types for sprk_aichatmessage and sprk_aichatsummary.
    </step>
    <step order="2" name="Create ChatSession and ChatMessage models">
      Create src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Models/Ai/Chat/ChatSession.cs:
      - SessionId, TenantId, DocumentId, PlaybookId, CreatedAt, LastActivity
      - Messages: IReadOnlyList&lt;ChatMessage&gt;

      Create ChatMessage.cs:
      - MessageId, SessionId, Role (User/Assistant/System), Content, TokenCount, CreatedAt
    </step>
    <step order="3" name="Create ChatSessionManager.cs">
      Create src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/ChatSessionManager.cs:
      - CreateSessionAsync(tenantId, documentId, playbookId) → ChatSession
      - GetSessionAsync(tenantId, sessionId) → ChatSession? (Redis first, Dataverse fallback)
      - DeleteSessionAsync(tenantId, sessionId)
      - Cache key: $"chat:session:{tenantId}:{sessionId}" with 24h sliding TTL
    </step>
    <step order="4" name="Create ChatHistoryManager.cs">
      Create src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Chat/ChatHistoryManager.cs:
      - AddMessageAsync(sessionId, message) → persists to Dataverse + updates Redis
      - GetHistoryAsync(sessionId, maxMessages=50) → recent messages
      - TriggerSummarizationAsync(sessionId) → if message count &gt;= 15, create summary
      - ArchiveHistoryAsync(sessionId) → when approaching 50 messages
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Register in Program.cs">
      Add: builder.Services.AddScoped&lt;ChatSessionManager&gt;();
      Add: builder.Services.AddScoped&lt;ChatHistoryManager&gt;();
      Update DI count in CLAUDE.md.
    </step>
    <step order="6" name="Write unit tests">
      Tests for:
      - CreateSession persists to Dataverse + caches in Redis
      - GetSession returns from Redis on hit, Dataverse on miss
      - AddMessage triggers summarization when count &gt;= 15
      - TTL is 24 hours
    </step>
    <step order="7" name="Verify build and tests">
      Run: dotnet build + dotnet test
      Both must pass.
    </step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="dotnet">Build and test</tool>
    <tool name="git">Stage changes</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
